OL,7,FWomen's rights campaigners including
OL,8,FFather Ted writer Graham Linehan were
OL,9,Fallegedly subjected to discrimination
OL,10,Fin a Belfast pub because of their
OL,11,Fgender critical beliefs, a court heard
OL,12,Ftoday.
OL,14,FCounsel for the group claimed they
OL,15,Fwere unlawfully refused service during
OL,16,Fa "hostile and febrile" encounter at
OL,17,FRobinson's Bar.
OL,19,FIt was also alleged that one of the
OL,20,Fcampaigners was assaulted and left
OL,21,Fwith a permanent facial scar.
